OL,3,CNUJ to intervene at tribunal over
OL,4,Cclaims of covert surveillance of
OL,5,Cjournalists
OL,7,FThe National Union of Journalists has
OL,8,Fbeen given the green light to take
OL,9,Fpart in a tribunal hearing over
OL,10,Fallegations of covert surveillance
OL,11,Fagainst two investigative reporters in
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland by the police.
OL,14,FThe Investigatory Powers Tribunal
OL,15,F(IPT) is due to hold a four-day
OL,16,Fhearing in the case brought by
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland-based filmmakers
OL,18,FBarry McCaffrey and Trevor Birney in
OL,19,FOctober over the claims.
