OL,7,FIn 2018, Mr McCaffrey and Mr Birney
OL,8,Fwere controversially arrested as part
OL,9,Fof a police investigation into the
OL,10,Falleged leaking of a confidential
OL,11,Fdocument that appeared in a film they
OL,12,Fmade on a Troubles massacre.
OL,14,FFormer PSNI chief constable Simon
OL,15,FByrne later unreservedly apologised
OL,16,Ffor how the men had been treated and
OL,17,Fthe PSNI agreed to pay #875,000 in
OL,18,Fdamages to the journalists and the
OL,19,Ffilm company behind the documentary.
