OL,7,FIn 2019, the pair lodged a complaint
OL,8,Fwith the IPT asking it to establish
OL,9,Fwhether there had been any unlawful
OL,10,Fsurveillance of them.
OL,12,FAt a preliminary hearing on Thursday,
OL,13,Fthe tribunal heard a bid from lawyers
OL,14,Ffor the NUJ to take part in the
OL,15,Fupcoming substantive hearing.
OL,17,FAhead of the hearing, Seamus Dooley,
OL,18,Fthe union's assistant general
OL,19,Fsecretary, said the bid was made over
OL,20,F"serious revelations which have caused
OL,21,Fsuch grave concern to our members".
