OL,7,FBrenda Campbell KC, for the NUJ, told
OL,8,Fthe tribunal in London that the case
OL,9,F"raises wider issues of public
OL,10,Fimportance" and that the union could
OL,11,Fadd aspects "distinct and of
OL,12,Fadditional value" to the hearing.
OL,14,FShe said: "There has been well-founded
OL,15,Fconcern amongst investigative
OL,16,Fjournalists, the Northern Irish public
OL,17,Fand spreading to the wider public
OL,18,Fabout unlawful surveillance of
OL,19,Fjournalists."
