OL,7,FThe barrister said that if the
OL,8,Fprotection of journalists' sources
OL,9,Fbecame "porous", then "who would risk
OL,10,Fbeing a source in those
OL,11,Fcircumstances?".
OL,13,FLord Justice Singh, Lady Carmichael
OL,14,Fand senior barrister Stephen Shaw KC
OL,15,Fsaid the union could put in written
OL,16,Fsubmissions of up to 25 pages.
