OL,7,FLord Justice Singh said: "We have
OL,8,Fconsidered that the appropriate and
OL,9,Fproportionate course would be to grant
OL,10,Fthe application by the NUJ to
OL,11,Fintervene in this case but only in
OL,12,Fwriting."
OL,14,FThe hearing comes after Northern
OL,15,FIreland's chief constable announced an
OL,16,Findependent review to examine
OL,17,Fallegations of the police surveillance
OL,18,Fof journalists.
